UD_ModOutcome_Evolution
ScriptName UD_ModOutcome_Evolution extends UD_ModOutcome

Device evolves

NameFull: Evolution

Parameters in DataStr (indices relative to DataStrOffset property): None

Form arguments: Form2  Device in to which will current device evolve. In case this is formlist, random device from formlist will be used.

Form3  Device in to which will current device evolve. In case this is formlist, random device from formlist will be used.

In case more then one FormX is filled, random one will be choosen
